
This directory contains the ZXPLOT graphics package developed
by Ming Xue with contributions from Zuojun Zhang. It's 
included inside the ARPS package for the convenience of
ARPS users. The authors reserve full rights to the package.
For problem or question, please contact Ming Xue, at 
mxue@ou.edu.


This direction contains only the minimum set of files for
ARPS package to work. For the full ZXPLOT package and
documents, please visit http://www.caps.ou.edu/ZXPLOT.
